---
description: Core project constraints for the Apple phone store
alwaysApply: true
---

Read the root `AGENTS.md` before non-trivial work.

This is a Laravel Blade SSR project using MySQL, Tailwind CSS, jQuery, and Font Awesome Free.

The official development environment is Windows with Laragon and PowerShell.

Use PowerShell-compatible commands. Do not require Docker, WSL, Linux, or macOS tooling.

Do not hard-code absolute Windows paths in application code.

Do not add React, Vue, Livewire, Inertia, Alpine.js, a separate frontend API, a search engine, online payment, reviews, comments, or a generic EAV system.

Keep the scope suitable for a university project.

Do not modify unrelated files.

For non-trivial tasks, plan first, implement a small vertical slice, run tests, and review the diff.

The catalog includes iPhone, iPad, iPod, and charging accessories.

All money uses integer Vietnamese đồng values.

jQuery is the default JavaScript library. You may suggest another library, but must not install it or modify package files until a human explicitly approves.
